Appointment Type Codes

CodeDescriptionCommentVersion
Complete A request to add a completed appointment, used to maintain records of completed appointments that did not appear in the schedule (e.g., STAT, walk-in, etc.)added v2.3
Normal Routine schedule request type – default if not valuedadded v2.3
Tentative A request for a tentative (e.g., “penciled in”) appointmentadded v2.3
